Order Granting Bail Modification.
It is hereby ordered that the defendant's bail bond be modified to a $5,000.00 personal recognizance bond to allow him to attend Sober Living Programs with placement in Lotus housing under the following conditions:
- there is an actual bed available;
- that he is released directly into the custody of a representative of Lotus House;
- that he is attending and meeting all program requirements;
- all other conditions remain the same.

